column5: OK, got my computer back tonight, seems my backup disks were no good so it is back to basics, still don't have email but should by tonight (I hope), got lots to do so I'll up date later.
and that's why we hate computers   well love/hate them
Welcome back to the interwebs, Cliff.
Now that you've had some time to prepare, how 'bout a walleye or bass report? Good to have you back.
Good to hear. If you need any computer help at all I'm sure there are a few geeks on here
